    On Wednesday, <purchabr>Sosnoff</purchabr> told the Securities and Exchange
Commission that he controls 13.6 pct of the company's stock.
    <purchabr>Sosnoff</purchabr> also informed the SEC that <acqabr>Caesars</acqabr> had offered to
buyout his holdings several times during the past year.
    No one from the <purchabr>Sosnoff</purchabr> organization was immediately
