    <acqabr>Caesars</acqabr> said its financial advisor, Drexel Burnham Lambert
Inc, had determined that <purchabr>Sosnoff</purchabr>'s offer was financially
inadequate for shareholders other than <purchabr>Sosnoff</purchabr>.
    The company said other factors it considered in rejecting
the offer were its financial condition, future prospects,
